langesS">s</c>t<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>piel der <rs ref="#pmb11201" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Duse</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr eingeengt bin.</p><closer>Mit freundlichen Grüßen<space unit="chars" quantity="5"/>Ihr<lb/><signed><handShift scribe="#pmb14328"/>Dr. Osc. Blumenthal</signed></closer><postscript><p><handShift/>Herrn<lb/><hi rend="latintype">Dr Arthur Schnitzler</hi><lb/><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb51" type="place">Wien I.</rs></hi></p><p>cop.</p></postscript></div></body><back><listPerson><tei:person xml:id="pmb14328">
